# Implementation Plan - Hierarchical Question Drill-Down Directory

We will refactor the **Question Bank Repository** (`admin-questions.tsx`) in the Admin Dashboard to support a highly premium **hierarchical drill-down directory**. Instead of displaying a dense and crowded accordion listing containing all questions of all classes simultaneously, the interface will offer a clean, three-step structured workflow:

1. **Step 1: Subjects Directory** — Shows a grid of all uploaded subjects with responsive fuzzy search filtering.
2. **Step 2: Class Directory** — Clicking a subject reveals a list of classroom levels (e.g. JSS1, SS2) that actually have questions uploaded under that subject.
3. **Step 3: Class Questions View** — Clicking a class redirects to a dedicated, high-fidelity view listing only the questions belonging to that specific Subject and Class. Includes term/type dropdowns, text searches, selection check boxes, bulk actions, and single/bulk editors.

